Module kivakit.kernel

Package com.telenav.kivakit.kernel.language.collections.list

package com.telenav.kivakit.kernel.language.collections.list
  • Class Summary
    Class
    Description
    BaseList<Element>
    A base class for bounded lists which adds a number of convenient methods as well as support for various KivaKit interfaces, including Indexable, Sequence, Addable, Appendable, Sized and CompressibleCollection.
    LinkedObjectList<T>
    A linked list of objects that adds functionality to LinkedList, including the ability to serialize with Kryo and to LinkedObjectList.compress(CompressibleCollection.Method) the collection to reduce consumed space (at which point it is no longer a mutable linked list).
    Lists
     
    ObjectList<Element>
    A bounded list of objects with overrides of methods from BaseList to downcast return values to ObjectList for convenience.
    StringList
    A list of strings, adding useful string operations to ObjectList.
    StringList.Converter
    Converts to and from a list of strings
